Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:29.48,ep,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无 风 日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你的快递
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.81,0:04:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 请在这里签名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.36,0:04:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 工作方面缺不缺人手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说想找个工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你就是大家说的那个宇宙少年吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:04:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找工作啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.54,0:05:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上个月正好有个人退休了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是已经雇了新人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.81,0:05:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓鱼的活儿肯定找得到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？ 没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为错过了洋流交汇带 最近一直都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:18.68,tips,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注：暖流与寒流的交汇地带往往渔业资源丰富
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到忙起来的时候 我会找你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.16,0:05:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在正忙着整理账单
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这活外行也干不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.40,0:05:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻宝呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地点倒是有了眉目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是还要过三天才能到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.93,0:05:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 害你期待了半天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多该去送快递了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我试着自己找看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:06:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 很好 很好 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.91,0:06:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微往上点 往上点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.68,0:06:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 都说是最上面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 左边  那边往左
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 做不来…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作的适用条件居然如此严格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber 数据库有更新吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍未找到适合贵官从事的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么情况？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰团的推进装置正在逐一停止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼欧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在那里傻站着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.31,0:07:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转换一下心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼欧 舰团停下了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.94,0:07:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没风了啦 没风
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.41,0:07:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 集合了 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.59,0:07:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这肉够大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.33,0:07:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足够大吃一顿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真亏你搞得到手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.73,0:07:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.14,0:07:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在搞派对没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易碰到无风日 应该有很多修理工作要做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:08:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混到我这个位置 手下干活的人要多少有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.30,0:08:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是弗兰基的船
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电源关掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我已经确认过了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 派对会场在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.73,0:08:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 刚刚那是皮尼欧的工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.49,0:08:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.96,0:08:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 因为无风日风平浪静
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以会选在这样的日子里维修船舶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.35,0:08:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰团会离开银河道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电力也会中断
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只有维修人员才能工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.30,0:08:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人则全都放假
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝贝尔 你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.37,0:08:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风景不赖吧 这可是绝佳位置
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 无风的海面就是这样的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.94,0:09:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱雅 梅露蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.59,0:09:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那里好像不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要游泳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞成！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德也来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.27,0:09:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.95,0:09:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.35,0:09:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别穿那件老土的衣服了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.71,0:09:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我脱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.63,0:09:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 身材挺棒嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥尔德姆医生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就打扰一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.57,0:10:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是费了好大劲才搞到的好肉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.97,0:10:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电力还没恢复啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.30,0:10:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 破废铁 你不能想点办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.05,0:10:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对象焚化完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞啥啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.93,0:10:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:10:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:10:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.91,0:11:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.41,0:11:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件事要交给你去办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.09,0:11:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.16,0:11:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去铁匠婆婆那里一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你去最合适
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.97,0:11:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这是只有你才能做到的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.81,0:11:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你要让雷德到那种地方去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.42,0:11:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然 谁让他浪费掉了一盘子的肉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是背后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德他不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里好痒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.93,0:11:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然痒吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:11:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.14,0:12:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下吃完烤肉又要发胖了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么「又要」啊 梅露蒂你根本不用担心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.65,0:12:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都有自己的标准嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.84,0:12:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有不少男生喜欢肉感的女生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.91,0:12:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是天真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.19,0:12:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,误会这点的话可是要吃苦头的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还 还是应该运动一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.06,0:12:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是莉吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.23,0:12:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.37,0:12:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.51,0:12:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起重机塔的喷水器你知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.21,0:12:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然电力恢复了 那东西却没动静
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.77,0:12:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 又坏了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能用冲浪风筝上去开启水泵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:44.40,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(558,650)}Surf Kite
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.87,0:12:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 我接下来要参加烤肉派对的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.65,0:12:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.13,0:12:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤肉？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.09,0:12:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 那么拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:12:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来比试一场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ok 我可不会输给你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来就不用担心发胖了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何在积极摄取食物的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又执着于维持体型
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的少女心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.54,0:13:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本机无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.51,0:13:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.75,0:13:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 要怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…破废铁 你很黑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.95,0:13:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 小弟弟你一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这脸蛋长得真甜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好嫩的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终点是起重机塔的顶端
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 升空的方法不要那么乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,询问采取该行动的必要性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.49,0:14:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼欧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我船上的绞盘你还修不修了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.17,0:14:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会修的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.05,0:14:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是工作忙得很吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意这些小事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.76,0:14:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一起吃吧 马上就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.13,0:14:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 别跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们这里工作怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber Chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉发生了紧急情况
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都叫你别动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对那家伙来说也算是有意义的社会实践
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本机表示同意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.73,0:15:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼欧 你在那做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.82,0:15:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么这身打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚刚在监督船底的检修
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 这里的电力什么时候才会恢复啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作没法按时完成 可能要停到傍晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没开始吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.07,0:15:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.63,0:15:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这身泳衣好大胆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新人不用承担业绩指标的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.21,0:15:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:15:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事 我到底做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:15:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一归我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.82,0:16:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定能成为我们店的头牌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.09,0:16:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 臀部曲线也很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有活力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.01,0:16:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体力也很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.43,0:16:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 总是艾米占甜头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是比赛就是比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.21,0:16:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一名归我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚好险呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 你怎么会在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.83,0:17:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我接着工作去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.78,0:18:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺着这条路走就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.66,0:18:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.54,0:18:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是场不错的运动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.81,0:18:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来就可以放开大吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.90,0:18:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,询问采取该行动的必要性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.15,0:18:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复 询问采取该行动的必要性…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:18:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多可以了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.76,0:19:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻人 你想要这个做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.57,0:19:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样就能解决的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.86,0:19:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是某种零件吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.20,0:19:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要回到那里去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 谁干的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把派对的事到处提
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.92,0:20:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.01,0:20:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 宇宙少年
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有盐总觉得不够味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.85,0:20:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.41,0:20:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 谁想要？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然婆婆的酱汁最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 不快吃就没了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.16,0:20:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.37,0:20:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也尝尝自己劳动的结晶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.80,0:21:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 起风了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.00,0:21:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 干活去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃饱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大概
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.90,0:21:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 毕竟你是途中才来的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 这场派对明明是为你准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.79,0:21:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 你没听说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为雷德一直没有找到工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼欧为了替你打气才特意安排的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.45,0:21:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.53,0:21:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你为大家努力工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.66,0:21:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 为大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.49,0:21:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏有你 大家才吃到了美味的烤肉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.70,0:21:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.81,0:21:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还会陪你一起去找工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.39,0:21:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道雷德哥哥适合什么工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.54,0:21:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该还是体力活吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛…不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.28,0:21:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.40,0:21:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 皮尼欧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.97,0:21:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你在这种地方偷懒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.85,0:22:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这可是名正言顺的工…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.97,0:22:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.83,0:22:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,询问采取该行动的必要性
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.57,0:22:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复 询问采取该行…
